W4lZOQLWK6A&oe=66EC0C58"}, {"file_name": "migrated_image.png", "id": "1669615673177303", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/12602284_986307178135757_74665936266723328_n.png?_nc_cat=101&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=GneRGuVHsG8Q7kNvgGG4j22&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=ARgSvwrC8GJr5hO0yi-dW18&oh=00_AYAcBECNzNBTSpQrfmtjFhJqbZcqwDjC5yJd4A3tVRSJ7g&oe=66EC1534"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": null, "display_name": "PhenomVR", "keywords": ["Electronmicroscopes", "SEM", "materialsscience", "imaging", "microscope"], "long_description": "Phenom-World is globally the yearly number 1 manufacturer of desktop scanning electron microscopes and analysis packages for a large scale of applications. The Phenom desktop SEM is known worldwide for its ease-of-use, speed and reliability.\nThe Phenom electron microscope is the ideal tool for investigating any sample and analyzing their composition in a short span of time. The rapid sample preparation and the incredibly short feedback time improve the efficiency and effectiveness of failure analysis, quality insurance processes, or non-destructive testing of materials.\nPhenom-World is based in the high-tech region of Eindhoven in The Netherlands. This strategic position and partners give Phenom-World access to the newest technologies and best resources for developing state-of-the-art equipment and applications. With representatives in more than 40 countries and a fast-growing installed base, we are committed to supporting our customers with a highly skilled team of specialists.", "short_description": "Phenom-World is globally the yearly number 1 manufacturer of desktop scanning electron microscopes and imaging and analysis packages required in a large variety of applications. The Phenom desktop SEM is known worldwide for its ease-of-use, speed and reliability.\n\nWith representatives in more than 40 countries and a fast-growing installed base, we are committed to supporting our customers wit